---
description: Core harness rules for Aidank-portfolio
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Read `AGENTS.md` first.
- Never edit `.next/` or `out/`; update source files and rebuild.
- Keep the site compatible with `output: "export"` and GitHub Pages deployment.
- Keep repository data in `lib/github.ts` and build-time generation, not client fetches.
- Prefer `config/site.ts` and `config/projects.ts` as the content source of truth.
- Run `npm run lint`, `npm run typecheck`, and, when relevant, `npm run build`.
